{"tid":587033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普捷天奴：祖雲達斯贏在向球證施壓","createTime":"2018-03-10T05:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T14:46:54.000Z","uid":103947,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4c75cbd30a7cf81a1b16d31af21927b454bd6b7e","tid":587033,"uid":103947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"「這種比賽要求表現以外既野。祖記係呢方面專家，因為佢地有贏既習慣，有向球證施壓既習慣。<br />\n<br />\n祖記班主Agnelli喺賽前同比賽中間都留喺隧道，祖記有一種不惜一切幫助球隊既文化。所以呢個機會我地不單喺場內，喺場外都學到野。對戰呢種球會係兩場戰役：一場場上踢，一場場外踢。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話利維都要企喺隧道，純粹講祖記係行為模範。賽前就Agnelli，賽後就Agnelli加Marotta。我見到半場佢地點樣向球證施壓。呢種賽事好講究細節，尤其雙方都有機會贏波。我相信呢啲細節幫到球會達成我地所需。」<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Competitions demand different things. Juve are specialists, because they have the habit to win, the habit to put pressure on the referee.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The owner [Agnelli] stayed in the tunnel before and during the game. It&rsquo;s a club with a culture to try to do everything to help the team. It&rsquo;s a massive opportunity to learn not only on the pitch but outside it. It&rsquo;s two games against this type of club &ndash; one on the pitch, one outside of the pitch.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t say that Daniel [Levy, the Tottenham chairman] needs to be there [in the tunnel]. Only that Juventus was a massive lesson in how to behave. Before the game was Agnelli. After the game was Agnelli, Marotta. I saw at half-time how they put pressure on the referee. It&rsquo;s about small details that count a lot in this type of game &ndash; even games that both teams can win. I believe those details can help the club to achieve what we want.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"faf9ad7289bc58930ac1a3c2ccfb3bc37f7b0e7a","tid":587033,"uid":17492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑"},{"pid":"0bc07a64f4e95e25c52db84221880e81488e64a9","tid":587033,"uid":103947,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"向球證施壓 vs 想呃球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7324a7ddb0a8ee3fc6ac8e87232eb375691b8b","tid":587033,"uid":2582,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"話熱狗黑哨輸波抵死嗰啲<br />\n根本都未撚睇過波 ，唔知狙黑哨打假比獌仲有過之而無不及"},{"pid":"50ec7640bb3863b1837a2719e3aebb0ad1e1c260","tid":587033,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"即係話拳霸熱唔洗向球證施壓已經有特權，肥普屈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fcb4965d8bcd8a7dcdb3a4a9906cef41b04f2a","tid":587033,"uid":96941,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce44e4f9131a5d8b04ab0ea1ac759c29252a37ad","tid":587033,"uid":64689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"熱狗自己唔夠努力插水怪球證唔幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bb1c4971ec36d64d6f64d80d49c4e65d9b05cf","tid":587033,"uid":125470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ee7324a7ddb0a8ee3fc6ac8e87232eb375691b8b","tid":587033,"uid":2582,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"話熱狗黑哨輸波抵死嗰啲<br />\n根本都未撚睇過波 ，唔知狙黑哨打假比獌仲有過之而無不及"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 祖記未入波前 有球熱狗禁區炒跌人波皮都掂唔到 球證都已經無比到12碼啦 技不如仲懶地硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cda7a2971a6ce7a983faf9f04558a7b65fcfbd9","tid":587033,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"個場真係好多手球好多黃牌"},{"pid":"49065f899f03b0e367ce237ec08e8b26ee186f01","tid":587033,"uid":79181,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68bb1c4971ec36d64d6f64d80d49c4e65d9b05cf","tid":587033,"uid":125470,"like"